summary: An Ordinance providing for the laying off, extending and establishing of East Sixty-ninth Street, across a portion of the East one-half of the Northeast one-quarter of the Southeast one- quarter of the Southeast one-quarter (E 1/2 of NE 1/4 of SE 1/4 of SE 1/4) of Section Five (5), Township Twenty-five (250 North, Range Four (4) East W. M.; providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor, and providing that the payment of the cost of said improvement be made by special assessment upon the property specially benefited, in the manner provided by law.
